{"place_id": "google-place-d894fc5411", "place_name": null, "source_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rebirth/@25.0213738,121.5303775,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x3442a988e919f47d:0xc36d3628b077d501!8m2!3d25.021369!4d121.5329524!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F1ptvr89ww?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMxMS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D", "reviewer_name": "Chihying Huang", "review_text": "很有懷舊氛圍的深夜咖啡廳\n餐點的部分也很有個性\n\n但可能太有個性了我沒辦法…\n-\n📌個人喜好：6.0/10\n\n#台北深夜咖啡廳 #台北不限時咖啡廳", "star_rating": 5.0, "review_date_text": "2 週前", "owner_response_text": null, "owner_response_date": null, "scraped_at": "2026-03-14T09:47:04.469759+00:00", "review_unique_key": "d97ca6a5450ab112665f70573508a294c35ee9d585dc5e5d53543d241fb8eade", "review_date_estimated": null, "scrape_run_id": "20260314T094641Z", "review_language": null, "reviewer_profile_url": null, "likes_count": null, "raw_review_metadata": {"review_id": "Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3NWFqUXhSbFZFWlZSc1pWRkdRMVIzU2xCaGNsRRAB", "relative_date_text": "2 週前"}}
{"place_id": "google-place-d894fc5411", "place_name": null, "source_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rebirth/@25.0213738,121.5303775,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x3442a988e919f47d:0xc36d3628b077d501!8m2!3d25.021369!4d121.5329524!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F1ptvr89ww?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMxMS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D", "reviewer_name": "兔兔王", "review_text": "真誠的老闆\n菜單在黑板上\n如果看不清楚，可以請他們幫忙介紹\n烹飪時間稍久，急性子或很餓的人不建議去他家\n這間店有自己的節奏\n我跟朋朋都覺得相當chill😌\n有點像漫畫或是古董店\n店內很多器具都是老闆組裝的\n像是門口那個酷酷的遊戲機\n喜歡那個花邊的陶碗\n蟹粉煲很好吃\n有點意外，布丁上居然加了哈密瓜", "star_rating": 5.0, "review_date_text": "5 個月前", "owner_response_text": null, "owner_response_date": null, "scraped_at": "2026-03-14T09:47:08.011712+00:00", "review_unique_key": "94a3235d7b584ee5ebfbb20c787ba71686c153b8c66e7574df3dcfeb8ef15949", "review_date_estimated": null, "scrape_run_id": "20260314T094641Z", "review_language": null, "reviewer_profile_url": null, "likes_count": 1, "raw_review_metadata": {"review_id": "Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2twSVUyOTBiVk5IYzFKTWVWVXhaVlZ1TnpGVGNtYxAB", "relative_date_text": "5 個月前"}}
{"place_id": "google-place-d894fc5411", "place_name": null, "source_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rebirth/@25.0213738,121.5303775,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x3442a988e919f47d:0xc36d3628b077d501!8m2!3d25.021369!4d121.5329524!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F1ptvr89ww?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMxMS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D", "reviewer_name": "Sheng Li", "review_text": "有種神秘感的舊舊咖啡店，裡面有滿滿的漫畫，有些應該是港版（？但種類是真的豐富，而且完全就是被大家翻爆看爆那種的痕跡，老板也很怪什麼都能聊，但他很忙，因為六點多會開始出餐，他會先在牆壁上寫今日的菜單，大家再分別點，一份份現做要等很久，但超愛他做的料理，氛圍很爽，就是會有一些酷酷集團或emo文青窩在這邊，如果要工作到很晚也可以來，下午三點營業到半夜，有各種類型的人，也會抽煙或一點點油煙味，但這就是這間店的魅力ㄅ，推推，但你可以不要來，我要來。", "star_rating": 5.0, "review_date_text": "1 年前", "owner_response_text": null, "owner_response_date": null, "scraped_at": "2026-03-14T09:47:12.899828+00:00", "review_unique_key": "b2cce54b1ed491e7c7f26a0407562657a6a72d52bec39f1db9a939c1dffcdeaf", "review_date_estimated": null, "scrape_run_id": "20260314T094641Z", "review_language": null, "reviewer_profile_url": null, "likes_count": 1, "raw_review_metadata": {"review_id": "ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURmOTlUWEdBEAE", "relative_date_text": "1 年前"}}
{"place_id": "google-place-d894fc5411", "place_name": null, "source_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rebirth/@25.0213738,121.5303775,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x3442a988e919f47d:0xc36d3628b077d501!8m2!3d25.021369!4d121.5329524!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F1ptvr89ww?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMxMS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D", "reviewer_name": "優質餐廳蒐藏家", "review_text": "☕️溫州街這一帶營業到深夜的咖啡廳。\n\n✅不限時！\n🛜有Wi-Fi。\n🔌大多數座位有插座（戶外無，部分座位要拉延長線）。\n💡燈光偏暗，不過有些座位有檯燈可以補光。\n🕑營業到凌晨兩點。\n📖有大量的漫畫，不少是有些年代的作品！\n🍴有提供種類很多樣的鹹食、正餐。\n💦水是一次給一大瓶，很方便！\n\n先講比較大的缺點：環境。\n氣氛其實是不錯的，感覺是老屋改建，老書櫃、老書桌、放著有些的年代的漫畫和遊戲機，整體氛圍是挺復古懷舊的。但環境是真的偏擁擠也有點兒髒，尤其是廁所，感覺真的很陳年老屋感，抽風機的聲音大到嚇人，旁邊水管還會漏水🤯\n\n撇除環境髒舊和空間擁擠以外，這家店其實不錯，不限時有插座，而且價格相當地平易近人，飲料很多都在150以下、餐點大多也在300元以內，以不限時咖啡廳來說並不貴（2024.8月價格，菜單在黑板上手寫板書，但有些很混亂有些字糊掉了，因此很難拍好）。\n這次雖然沒點鹹食餐點，但聞到其他人的餐點真的很香，而我自己點的飲料桂花紅玉鮮奶茶雖然有點稀，但喝起來還不賴。\n\n服務的部分這次體驗也很不錯，遇到的店員蠻親切的！", "star_rating": 4.0, "review_date_text": "1 年前", "owner_response_text": null, "owner_response_date": null, "scraped_at": "2026-03-14T09:47:17.706153+00:00", "review_unique_key": "fda43ef669b8b6c2b543e29f96fcf4bc1f18c5b78b700d7edb9baab2c03bdb7d", "review_date_estimated": null, "scrape_run_id": "20260314T094641Z", "review_language": null, "reviewer_profile_url": null, "likes_count": 2, "raw_review_metadata": {"review_id": "ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURiX1oyN1h3EAE", "relative_date_text": "1 年前"}}
{"place_id": "google-place-d894fc5411", "place_name": null, "source_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rebirth/@25.0213738,121.5303775,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x3442a988e919f47d:0xc36d3628b077d501!8m2!3d25.021369!4d121.5329524!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F1ptvr89ww?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMxMS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D", "reviewer_name": "Eva", "review_text": "交通部分：位於公館商圈附近 巷弄內機車停放算方便 大眾運輸工具需步行約五分鐘\n\n環境部分：桌間距離偏小 內部環境整牆的漫畫書 復古的遊戲機滿滿的特色\n菜單呈現於牆上 有不懂的都可以詢問店員\n店員服務親切 也很熱心說明內容\n\n⚠️唯一美中不足店外偶有抽菸的人～\n會有一陣一陣的煙味\n\n餐點部分：餐點有老闆一人料理！\n主餐炸牛排調味很棒！前菜的生魚塊 很新鮮～\n最推薦的！！肉桂捲 無可挑剔的甜點\n肉桂 不會被上面的奶油搶戲\n會想一直去吃的甜點❤️", "star_rating": 4.0, "review_date_text": "1 年前", "owner_response_text": null, "owner_response_date": null, "scraped_at": "2026-03-14T09:47:22.359720+00:00", "review_unique_key": "2c11620a515d242d9cef717f2baf8a579f109ae85f04e0200e9979c49eb4ad5e", "review_date_estimated": null, "scrape_run_id": "20260314T094641Z", "review_language": null, "reviewer_profile_url": null, "likes_count": null, "raw_review_metadata": {"review_id": "ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUREdjZtTW93RRAB", "relative_date_text": "1 年前"}}
